title: An Update from Carrie Lynn from Yesterday
description: Carrie Lynn called us yesterday to tell us that she's pregnant and due on Monday and the baby might not be her husband's and if it isn't, it would be bi-racial.  She called us back today to let us know if she's going to tell her husband or just hope that the baby is his.
